50|$|A front <b>suspension</b> <b>fork</b> {{is common}} on high-end, contemporary-styled European city bikes. This {{is often a}} coil/oil or air/oil <b>suspension</b> <b>fork</b> with {{adjustable}} compression and rebound. A traditional roadster has no front suspension, or a spring-based front suspension that has more limited travel and adjustability.|$|E
